  <description>
    <p>Open Lighting Console is a free software to control lights on theater shows.</p>
    <p>Some features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Used sACN or Open Lighting Architecture to send DMX</li>
      <li>RPN syntax</li>
      <li>Import / Export ASCII Light Cue shows</li>
      <li>Patch / Unpatch by channels or by outputs</li>
      <li>Main Playback</li>
      <li>Chasers</li>
      <li>Groups</li>
      <li>Faders</li>
      <li>Track channels</li>
      <li>Virtual console with easy MIDI learning for controllers</li>
      <li>Open Sound Control</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
